## Import

An existing SKS node pool may be imported by `<cluster-ID>/<nodepool-ID>@<zone>`:

```shell
terraform import \
  exoscale_sks_nodepool.my_sks_nodepool \
  f81d4fae-7dec-11d0-a765-00a0c91e6bf6/9ecc6b8b-73d4-4211-8ced-f7f29bb79524@ch-gva-2
```
